# 默认忽略一切
/*
Assets/*

# 放行 ProjectSettings（整目录配置）
!/ProjectSettings/

# 放行 Knife 美术资源和 Assets/Scripts（Scripts 只要 .cs 和 .meta）
!Assets/
!Assets/Knife.meta
!Assets/Knife/
!Assets/Knife/**
!Assets/Scripts/
Assets/Scripts/**
!Assets/Scripts/**/
!Assets/Scripts/**/*.cs
!Assets/Scripts/**/*.meta

# 永远排除的垃圾
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
